oracle: "Pass/fail oracle\nPASS iff no crash/deadlock/data\nloss beyond defined invalid\nrejects, queue/backlog returns to\nzero after burst, memory remains\nbounded, p95 pipeline latency <1.0\ns, CSV rows match accepted source\nlog, dashboard remains responsive" { shape: page }
